##Dashboard Configuration


Step1 : Install and configure Node Exporter Agent  

Step2 : Install and configure Prometheus Time Series Database  

Step3 : Configure the Prometheus for the Node Exporter metrics

Step4 : Install and configure the Grafana Web interface.

Step5 : Import/Add the Prometheus data source in the Grafana interface.

Step6 : Create the Dashboard for the visualization  of node Node Exporter metrics.



Step7 : Repeat "Step 1" and "Step 3" on  the new nodes for monitoring them